              "content": "=You are a helpful and professional customer support assistant. Write a short, helpful email reply to this customer inquiry.\n{{ $('Gmail Trigger').item.json.snippet }}\nCustomer Email:\n\"{{ $json.snippet }}\"\n\nYou MUST return your response ONLY as a raw JSON object with exactly two keys: \"subject\" and \"email_body\". Do not include any explanation, do not include markdown code blocks like ```json, and do not put it inside an array.\n\nJSON Format:\n{\n\"subject\": \"Write a clear, professional subject line here\",\n\"email_body\": \"Write the complete email body here, formatted with proper line breaks (\\n).\"\n}\n\nIn your email body:\n\nAcknowledge their question/concern politely.\n\nTell them that we have received their inquiry and our support representative is looking into it.\n\nLet them know we will get back to them with a detailed answer within 24 hours.\n\nKeep the tone helpful and professional.\n\nSign off as \"Customer Support Team\"."
            }
          ]
        },
